flowchart LR
  WS["nixos-ws (workstation)<br>Darwin"]
  HL[nixos-homelab<br>NixOS]
  VPS[nixos-vps<br>NixOS]
  CACHE[(binary cache<br>Attic/Cachix/...)]

  %% Stage 2: reuse build artifacts (two options)

  %% Option A: Global reuse via cache
  HL -->|push artifacts| CACHE
  VPS -->|pull/substitute| CACHE

  %% Option B: Reuse without cache (point-to-point)
  HL -->|nix-copy-closure<br>store paths| VPS

  %% Control plane (deploy/activate)
  WS -->|deploy / activate| HL
  WS -->|deploy / activate| VPS
